result.name: roosecote-sands-and-east-of-walney-island-map-of-zostera-beds
result.notes: This map shows the area covered by seagrass beds to the east of Walney Island and in Roosecote Sands (both areas are west of Morecambe Bay). The data were obtained by the MESH Project as the results of a data collation contract undertaken by OSPAR.
